platformAttributes.ios.subtitle.k: 一個平靜，引人注目的益智遊戲

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.st.k: Stunning doesn’t even begin to describe it. In this unique puzzler, the animations are just as rewarding as the gameplay. We never got tired of watching the board unfold in a blossom of colourful origami. Our favourite new feature? An editor that lets you create your own gorgeous puzzles and share them with the world.

platformAttributes.ios.editorialNotes.sh.k: We loved playing with these paper puzzles - every fold is a tactile delight.
